reviewText: It's a fun and educational video.
This is the first in a new DVD series for youngsters. They can learn and have fun at the same time. I'm looking forward to purchasing more in this series for the library.

I purchased Teddy P. Brains several months ago on a hummer, having just seen it in a store and not known anything about it.  My children and I enjoyed it very much and have watched it countless times!  This is a great story, with a very positive and inspiring message.  I cannot wait for the next episode!
